data.value:
Meet our marvelous Congrats Grad! Mug - a gift that'll remind the shining star of their accomplishments, wherever they go! With the option to personalize our premium mug with your favorite photo - this heartfelt gift makes the perfect pick, for the graduate about to set out on their new journey.
A customized mug is sure to be a statement piece on your shelf. Printed with heat transfer printing. The color is coated in outer appearance only.
